Great migration
A '''great migration''' is a mass exodus of users from one online community to another, usually as a result of drama.

Of course, the axiom "whereever you go, there you are" applies, thus guaranteeing that the new community will be as drama-laden as the old.

== Famous mass exodii in history ==
*[http://www.livejournal.com/userinfo.bml?user=ljdrama The LJDrama community] on livejournal migrated to the [http://ljdrama.org ljdrama.org] website after it was suspended, thus providing even stronger [[lulz]] than ever before.

